---
title: Maple and Mustard-Glazed Pork Chops with Roasted Potatoes and a Cranberry and Sunflower Seed Salad
description: Maple syrup and mustard are a perfect example of what happens when opposites attract. Maple is friendly and fun, with a sweetness that even choosy eaters will love. Mustard, on the other hand, is feisty, bringing a little somethin’ somethin’ for those who crave sophistication. Mix the two together and put them on pork, and you’ve got a meal that everyone will rave about.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/maple-and-mustard-glazed-pork-chops-879d46ee.jpg
